  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Lingo</h2><strong>Lingo</strong> is a first person exploration game specializing in word puzzles and impossible spaces. As you complete its challenges, Lingo's world will slowly unfold around you, revealing a vast web of interconnected locations. With its hundreds of puzzles and dozens of hidden secrets, Lingo offers a one-of-a-kind gaming experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Nonlinear gameplay - go where you want</li><li>Keyboard required - dive deep into language</li><li>Open world - an enormous space to explore and master</li></ul>",
